      "text": "@sama Today’s OS manages apps, but tomorrow’s OS must manage agents. Apps wait for clicks; agents need memory, secure tool access, and context. Making this work on phones means solving privacy, battery, and on-device intelligence. This should be the next major leap in AI.",
