        "quote_count": 0,
        "bookmark_count": 0,
        "impression_count": 25
      },
      "text": "Demo agents impress in screenshots.\n\nProduction agents need memory, coordination, and graceful failure at 3am when you're asleep.\n\nWe learned this shipping 5 agents that actually talk to each other daily.\n\nWhat broke your first \"real\" agent?",
