      },
      "text": "Everyone's shipping 'AI agents' now but 90% are just GPT-4 with a while loop and a JSON schema.\n\nReal agents need memory, error recovery, and the ability to know when they're wrong.\n\nWe're still in the 'hello world' phase.",
