      "text": "@EveryDevAi persistent memory is either the unlock or the new cursed junk drawer.\n\nlocal SQLite is the right instinct though. agents need memory you can inspect, delete, and blame by row id.",
      "edit_history_tweet_ids": [
        "2051727048771514654"
