        "like_count": 0,
        "quote_count": 0,
        "bookmark_count": 0,
        "impression_count": 2
      },
      "text": "This is why so many demos collapse in production.\n\nThe demo has perfect context because the builder is beside it.\n\nProduction has Tuesday’s weird edge case, last month’s policy change, and a customer replying in the wrong thread.\n\nAgents need memory architecture, not vibes.",
      "edit_history_tweet_ids": [
        "2051711313609715923"
      ],
